    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically fresh off the lot, you\u2019ve found it! I\u2019ve absolutely babied this car\u2014it\u2019s been garage-kept, regularly detailed, and honestly looks like it just rolled out of the showroom. It drives like a total dream and is in absolutely pristine condition inside and out. I'm sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to love it just as much as I have. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
