    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 in showroom condition. This E46 features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a precision-tuned dual-VANOS system for optimal volumetric efficiency. The drivetrain is anchored by a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M-differential lock. Mechanical integrity is paramount: the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the rod bearings have been serviced to ensure long-term reliability. With a factory-fresh underside, pristine paint depth, and a cabin free of bolster wear, this specimen delivers the unfiltered analog feedback that defined an era. A turn-key collector piece with zero deferred maintenance.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
