    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that redefines the standard for mint condition. This meticulously maintained masterpiece has been exclusively garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and professionally detailed, preserving its original showroom luster. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with a premium ceramic coating, completely free of stone chips, door dings, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains in 'time-capsule' state; the high-grade leather upholstery is supple and entirely free of wear or creasing, while the original carpets have been protected by heavy-duty mats since day one. Every electronic component, from the infotainment system to the seat heaters, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a documented full service history exclusively through authorized dealerships. With remarkably low mileage and a recent set of high-performance tires, it delivers a driving experience that is as tight, quiet, and responsive as the day it was first delivered. This is an collector-quality example for the most discerning buyer who demands perfection.",
